projectDescription: This was my graduation project, We developed it using flutter framework, our application consists of two main parts: First part the learning part where the user can use it to learn the basics of the Arabic sign language. Second part is the translation part where the user can upload a video or capture a video then the video is sent to the server to translate it and returns the response back in the form of Arabic text( handled using API request).

I participated in developing this application with my colleagues. It's a coffee shop application where all the menu contents are available in the application with the price of every item according to it's size and the user can also search for a specific item with its name, the user can also add, remove items to his favorites list. We also created an admin panel so we can add, remove, update items to the application. We used firebase for user's authentication and as a backend for the app data and users data and also for authentication.
